{"tid":1739451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致各因投降感到抱歉嘅人士","createTime":"2019-11-19T14:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T02:00:18.000Z","uid":332021,"like":45,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0969fd7a4448fa6ac4fe66e0b188e37902ef0d40","tid":1739451,"uid":332021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"見到有小朋友自己走咗岀嚟，之後全部都係歉意。想回覆但好開心已經搵唔返個po。<br />\n<br />\n但我想講：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收嗲啦，唔關你地事呀，全部都係黑警同港共嘅錯呀！<br />\n<br />\n唔洗內疚唔洗對唔住，唔洗理岀面班人講乜。事關佢地全部都係馬後炮事後孔明<br />\n<br />\n戰爭係每個人盡本份先有戰果，可能你可以做更多，但我地岀面所有手足都係！呢個責任係全部人嫁！<br />\n<br />\n每個人都懦弱，但記住懦弱唔係錯；懦弱先教到人堅強。<br />\n<br />\n你地已經做得夠多，你地燒咗銳武、當晚所有嘅行動，都成為手足心中嘅旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n身為手足個個都希望其他手足人身安全無事為重，條命喺度先做到世界冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有正因手足唔係condom，唔係話幾多人換幾多人先化算嘅效益主義！所以唔好介意有幾多人救你地，因為好多手足岀去果時基本無介意過！<br />\n<br />\n因為你地，香港人尋日先搵反自己嘅鬥志。都造就左個機會話俾所有手足聽：we never alone<br />\n<br />\n尋日所有和理非都無退過。因為咩呀？因為你地埋咗個旗幟係大家心入邊呀。<br />\n呢啲就係最豐實嘅戰果。<br />\n<br />\n明白內疚會追住大家，但唔好俾內疚打沉你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n岀事嘅手足而家暫時退一退火線都係保障自己，<br />\n如果無論如何都想岀分力，請將革命宣揚開去，保持前線嘅後勤，文宣追唔上變化都係呢場運動好多人愈嚟愈忽略嘅位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"f8138f94f9497115cf72bf98cff642b18153fb34","tid":1739451,"uid":124763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"254e93373a521c0cc6500c1cf678c1aee0284188","tid":1739451,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:02:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67f63098c5885cccc8fba6969bd6dbc5e42db34e","tid":1739451,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:02:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4947731ef65a385243724a8f03496bdade64cfcf","tid":1739451,"uid":338636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:03:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>入嚟睇致勝關鍵！！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[拒絕分化！]古人一早教我地點贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>全個連登都係負能量，我要你地有正能量啊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ac029e38cdb16603a2b73aee0f644c532f652b54","tid":1739451,"uid":332021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8138f94f9497115cf72bf98cff642b18153fb34","tid":1739451,"uid":124763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:03:32.000Z","msg":"多謝，p牌仔第一次比人推"},{"pid":"83ffcbc13fdc461c9ffe9fca0b9992c58d53153e","tid":1739451,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"錯手負咗評<br />\n手足, 永遠一起向前!"},{"pid":"92fc64ed862dce568212c6633e3ab70851b3d3b8","tid":1739451,"uid":278311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:04:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1738999/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1738999/page/1</a><br />\n面對現實，長期抗爭，分工合作"},{"pid":"a7c72d6b867aa98b331305f0107fd22d1ab8e6f9","tid":1739451,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5141e1b227659e9a56ae4629f6cb1e3814813ec","tid":1739451,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:15:47.000Z","msg":"士氣+1<br />\n推"},{"pid":"84175b5593a02cd0a4a3f253ee9a6f771e8b6df3","tid":1739451,"uid":332021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83ffcbc13fdc461c9ffe9fca0b9992c58d53153e","tid":1739451,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"